/images/cache/b47e9fc43b36df3fbd5a626a3f2ed791_w263_h263.jpg 263w" alt="" itemprop=thumbnailUrl /> </div><header class="article-header clearfix"><h2 class=article-title itemprop=headline> <a href=/britain-socialist-appeal-national-conference-celebrates-revolutionary-times.htm itemprop=url title="Britain: Socialist Appeal national conference celebrates revolutionary times"> Britain: Socialist Appeal national conference celebrates revolutionary times</a> </h2></header><aside class="article-aside clearfix"><dl class="article-info  muted"> <dt class=article-info-term> Details </dt><dd class="createdby hasTooltip" itemprop=author itemscope itemtype=http://schema.org/Person title="Written by "> <i class="fa fa-user"></i> <span itemprop=name>Socialist Appeal (UK)</span> </dd><dd class="published hasTooltip" title="Published: "> <i class=icon-calendar></i> <time datetime=2018-03-20T11:48:55+00:00 itemprop=datePublished> 20 March 2018 </time> </dd> </dl> </aside><section class="article-intro clearfix"><p>One decade on from the onset of the Great Recession, and British society is undergoing a series of crises: economic, political, and social. The status quo has broken; the centre ground has collapsed; political polarisation and radicalisation is taking place everywhere.</p></section></article></div></div><div class=col-md-6><div class="items-row cols-1 row-0 row"><div class="item column-1 col-md-12"><article><div class=featured-text> <header class="article-header clearfix"><h2 class=article-title itemprop=headline> <a href=/south-africa-meaningful-land-reform-means-fighting-for-socialism.htm itemprop=url title="South Africa: meaningful land reform means fighting for socialism!"> South Africa: meaningful land reform means fighting for socialism!</a> </h2></header><aside class="article-aside clearfix"><dl class="article-info  muted"> <dt class=article-info-term> Details </dt><dd class="createdby hasTooltip" itemprop=author itemscope itemtype=http://schema.org/Person title="Written by "> <i class="fa fa-user"></i> <span itemprop=name>Ben Morken</span> </dd><dd class="published hasTooltip" title="Published: "> <i class=icon-calendar></i> <time datetime=2018-03-19T15:32:22+00:00 itemprop=datePublished> 19 March 2018 </time> </dd> </dl> </aside><div class=featured-image><div class="pull-right item-image"> <a href=/south-africa-meaningful-land-reform-means-fighting-for-socialism.htm><img src=/images/cache/10b9ea79a68fac4d20402192f51bbf07_w100_h100_cp.jpg alt="" itemprop=thumbnailUrl /></a> </div></div><section class="article-intro clearfix"> On 27 February, the National Assembly of South Africa passed a motion on land expropriation, tabled by the Economic Freedom Fighters and supported by the majority of parties in parliament, including the ANC. Ben Morken in... </section></div></article></div></div><div class="items-row cols-1 row-1 row"><div class="item column-1 col-md-12"><article><div class=featured-text> <header class="article-header clearfix"><h2 class=article-title itemprop=headline> <a href=/usa-west-virginia-teachers-victory-shows-workers-fighting-back.htm itemprop=url title="USA: West Virginia teachers' victory shows workers fighting back!"> USA: West Virginia teachers' victory shows workers fighting back!</a> </h2></header><aside class="article-aside clearfix"><dl class="article-info  muted"> <dt class=article-info-term> Details </dt><dd class="createdby hasTooltip" itemprop=author itemscope itemtype=http://schema.org/Person title="Written by "> <i class="fa fa-user"></i> <span itemprop=name>Socialist Revolution (USA)</span> </dd><dd class="published hasTooltip" title="Published: "> <i class=icon-calendar></i> <time datetime=2018-03-19T13:10:06+00:00 itemprop=datePublished> 19 March 2018 </time> </dd> </dl> </aside><div class=featured-image><div class="pull-right item-image"> <a href=/usa-west-virginia-teachers-victory-shows-workers-fighting-back.htm><img src=/images/cache/0adfe4a77a0d5308906bf600a048d667_w100_h100_cp.JPG alt="" ite